# AllFantasy Prompt Contract

When the user asks for development prompts, output must follow this contract:

- copy-paste ready
- one prompt per fenced code block
- production prompt style
- clearly structured instructions
- include mandatory supported sports requirements
- include mandatory UI click-audit requirements
- include QA requirements

Do not output half-structured prompts.

If multiple prompts are requested, provide multiple fenced blocks, one prompt per block.
